data.description: Must see home situated on a level lot in a quiet neighborhood in Good Hope which is located in southern Harrison County.  The home includes a large Family Room with a hardwood floor, bar, large flat screen TV w/Bose surround sound, indoor hot-tub and leather seating with recliners built-in.  This is a great room for entertaining friends and family.  The home will include all appliances.  In addition, the living room will include a couch, recliner and armoire with a flat screen TV.  There is a gas fireplace located in the living room as well.  The home includes a large kitchen which is great for preparing your Holiday gatherings.  The home has been well maintained and is move-in ready.  You must view this home to appreciate everything there is to offer.
